item.title: Javac
item.dc:creator: @sexy_slay sexy slay
item.description:
@sexy_slay wrote:

It makes perfect sense, Does “javac is not recognized as an internal or external command” sound familiar. Basically you haven’t set your environmental variables for Java yet. If you have a PC, it should be Control Panel -> Java -> Java (the tab) -> View

After this i would recommend finding one of the many tutorials on environmental variables.

And Eson, don’t say stuff doesn’t make sense if you have little knowledge of java.
Thanks
-Sexy Slay
